CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three women, including one standing on right wearing dark skirt, and light colored sweater with tab at neck, and two men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence seated at desk, signing document, gathered in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
